        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0003",
      "text": "rent Bit Error Rate reporting parameters being enforced.  If no Bit Error Rate reporting is being",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        57.65,
        539.91,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0004",
      "text": "enforced, words 2 and 3 shall be set to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        69.65,
        319.04,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0005",
      "text": "4.2.41",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        123.78,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0006",
      "text": "Report Port Speed Capabilities (RPSC)",
      "bbox": [
        133.84,
        94.97,
        317.59,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0007",
      "text": "4.2.41.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        192.63,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0008",
      "text": "The RPSC ELS shall provide a method for a Port to report its current and potential link operating",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        539.96,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0009",
      "text": "speeds.  The normal response to an RPSC ELS Sequence shall be a LS_ACC ELS Sequence.  If the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        539.94,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0010",
      "text": "recipient Port does not support the RPSC ELS, it shall reply with an LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        539.89,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0011",
      "text": "reason code of \"Command not supported\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        284.77,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0012",
      "text": "4.2.41.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        178.22,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0013",
      "text": "a) RPSC Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        226.96,
        237.88,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0014",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        250.96,
        287.89,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0015",
      "text": "4.2.41.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        227.06,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0016",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        157.1,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0017",
      "text": "The S_ID designates the source port that is requesting port speeds.  The D_ID field",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        298.96,
        539.97,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0018",
      "text": "designates the recipient that is to process the RPSC request.  If the recipient is a Domain Controller,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        540.12,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0019",
      "text": "the request is for all the ports within that domain.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        310.96,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0020",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        140.41,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0021",
      "text": "The format of the RPSC Payload is shown in table 112.",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        346.96,
        384.85,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0022",
      "text": "4.2.41.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        214.86,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0023",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        138.19,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0024",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies the rejection of the RPSC Request",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        478.96,
        368.69,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0025",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        142.05,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p126_s0026",
      "text": "LS_ACC signifies acceptance of the RPSC Request and its Accept Payload.  The format",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        502.96,
        539.97,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
